Class BaseGeneralRecipe.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zeitheron.hammercore.api.crafting.impl.BaseGeneralRecipe.Builder

    BaseGeneralRecipe

    public static class BaseGeneralRecipe.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    A Builder class for BaseGeneralRecipe. allows to register inputs, fluids, energy and set output for a recipe, then build it.
